description: All season custom auto mats that are non-fading and non-cracking. These mats have tremendous liquid holding capacity and will also keep debris, sand, mud and rocks in place within the hexo shaped pockets. The mats have a unique hexo-shaped border to border design. An exclusively developed compound gives the Hexomat a rubber feel and look, and the non-skid nib backing provides optimum traction. Manufactured in USA. All season custom auto mats meet all the standards and requirements. Over 10,000 custom fit patterns, including: full front overalls, rear overalls, cargo/trunk mats for all SUVs mini vans and sedans. All patterns are computer precision cut to guarantee the highest consistency in design and fit. Available in tan, black, gray, clear and ivory. Lifetime warranty.

Molded from a space-age rubber composite, Intro-Tech Automotive Hexomat Floor Mats are both flexible and durable. This unique material means Hexomat car mats won't fade, crack or otherwise deteriorate. They're custom-contoured to the shape of your floor pan for maximum coverage in a low-profile design, with no clumsy tall outer rim.

Hexomat car mats come in a range of five universal colors sure to match or highlight your vehicle's interior and are designed to fit almost any vehicle. Available for the front and back, and including a variety of cargo and trunk mats, each piece is sold separately. Not all mats are available for all vehicles.
